<TEXT>This car is an absolute adrenaline rush to drive. Until something breaks. I have to take it in 6 times for rattles. Dash rattle, chair squeaks and build quality issues are rampant. I thought Japanese cars were supposed to built better than this. My old Hyundai had 0 rattles. What gives, Mazda? I thought the 5 door styling would grow on me. It didn't. Very poor choice.</TEXT>
